  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da0\u0dca\u0da0\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dc5\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two dead bodies are found on the side of the train road",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mirigama police say that the bodies of two people who fell down and died on the side of the narrow railway between Ambepussa and Bothale railway stations were found.",
        "The police also say that these two, who were dressed in sarams and shirts, appear to be quite old.",
        "The police are working to find out whether the two were hit by the train while they were on the side of the narrow track or fell from any train."
      ],
